Package: shinysurveyjs
Title: Create and Deploy Survey Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dylan", "Pieper", , "dylanpieper@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of this package is to integrate 'SurveyJS' <https://surveyjs.io/> 
    with 'Shiny' <https://shiny.posit.co/> to interface with 'MySQL' and other DBI databases
    and create dynamic user experiences.
